# QualityMind - Meet the Minds Day


## Prepare and run project

1. Switch into angular app directory
cd {project.root}/src/icecream-app
# initialize angular project
2. npm install
# compile and run server (http://localhost:4200)
3. npm start

# build backend
1. Switch into project root directory
2. mvn clean install

# install Open Liberty, configure it, deploy application and start the server (noch nicht ausprobiert)
mvn package -P install-open-liberty
mvn package -P configure-open-liberty (noch nicht fertig)
mvn liberty:start

